# ESP32 Ultrasonic Bluetooth Speaker

## Description
Bluetooth A2DP sink that demodulates audio into an ultrasonic AM PWM carrier.

## Features
- Bluetooth A2DP (SBC)
- Envelope detection
- 40 kHz ultrasonic PWM carrier

## Hardware
- ESP32-WROOM-32E
- Ultrasonic transducer + driver

## Build
```bash
platformio run -t upload
```

## Notes
- Phone volume controls loudness
- Envelope-only audio (speech optimized)
